### Circle webhook simulation - initial delivery
POST http://localhost:5000/api/webhooks/circle
Content-Type: application/json
x-amz-sns-message-id: TEST-MSG-1

{
	"Type": "Notification",
	"MessageId": "TEST-MSG-1",
	"SigningCertURL": "https://sns.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/SimpleNotificationService.pem",
	"Signature": "dev-signature",
	"payload": {
		"event": "gateway.mint.finalized",
		"amount": 500,
		"walletAddress": "0xDEVTESTAGENT0000000000000000000000000000",
		"agentId": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111"
	}
}

